<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="that-adj">that <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ðæt/    美 /ðæt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>那；那个：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The shy, quiet freshman achieved success that year.
那个害羞的、不爱说话的新生那年取得了成功。</p><footer>2010 北京</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>那样的；如此的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He was angry to that degree that he turned pale.
他怒火中烧，脸色苍白。</p></div></div>